comments: Antetokounmpo (MIL) lowers his shoulder into the body of Westbrook (WAS) and dislodges him from his position during his post up.
Holiday (MIL) maintains his position in bounds as he saves the ball.
Lopez (MIL) momentarily places two hands on the back of Beal (WAS) and slightly extends them before rolling to the basket.  The contact is marginal and does not disrupts Beal's ability to defend.
Westbrook (WAS) legally contests Connaughton's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
Westbrook (WAS) legally contests Connaughton's (MIL) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Lopez (MIL) legally contests Beal's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Beal (WAS), firms up and absorbs the contact.
Connaughton (MIL) swipes down and makes contact across the arm of Gafford (WAS) as he he gathers in the post.
Holiday (MIL) cleanly blocks the layup attempt by Gafford (WAS).
Connaughton (MIL) cleanly blocks layup attempt by Gafford (WAS).
Neto (WAS) steals the inbound pass and then steps out of bounds.
